  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018830/extras/8ae42cf1509115735c3a3269be1d32d0.avif?t=1721041621\" width=666 height=66 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018830/extras/3501515a1dbd7a6b9f1eaae96d88146c.poster.avif?t=1721041621\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018830/extras/3501515a1dbd7a6b9f1eaae96d88146c.webm?t=1721041621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018830/extras/3501515a1dbd7a6b9f1eaae96d88146c.mp4?t=1721041621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018830/extras/be44f96f4fa16c62f7a8d3cf3d49d481.avif?t=1721041621\" width=666 height=66 /></span><br><br><strong>Your goal is to find the key to the locked door to get out of the house. A crazy Kawaii girl will stop you from doing this. For a while, you can hide from her in a barn chest, under a bed or in a closet, but in general, if she notices you, you better run. </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018830/extras/62b7185ee28546368119d5634922a344.poster.avif?t=1721041621\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018830/extras/62b7185ee28546368119d5634922a344.webm?t=1721041621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018830/extras/62b7185ee28546368119d5634922a344.mp4?t=1721041621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018830/extras/21a24beb13fa131d509f48184b87c670.avif?t=1721041621\" width=666 height=66 /></span><br><br><strong>In the main menu, you can choose one of the 14 characters that will chase you. Don't let them get to you!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018830/extras/c9d4d1a7af0b973adb1600a55a3d9abb.poster.avif?t=1721041621\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018830/extras/c9d4d1a7af0b973adb1600a55a3d9abb.webm?t=1721041621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018830/extras/c9d4d1a7af0b973adb1600a55a3d9abb.mp4?t=1721041621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018830/extras/dfcb28926c4e8026a1260bd5586f5e28.avif?t=1721041621\" width=666 height=66 /></span><br><br><strong>You are trapped in a country house with someone chasing you and you need to find a way out. This is a game about hide and seek in a confined space and you have five lives - that is, five attempts to open the door and escape. If you fail, the level will start over.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018830/extras/60541c3c4b31052b8ea10afd2b06f505.poster.avif?t=1721041621\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018830/extras/60541c3c4b31052b8ea10afd2b06f505.webm?t=1721041621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018830/extras/60541c3c4b31052b8ea10afd2b06f505.mp4?t=1721041621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018830/extras/8ae42cf1509115735c3a3269be1d32d0.avif?t=1721041621\" width=666 height=66 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018830/extras/3501515a1dbd7a6b9f1eaae96d88146c.poster.avif?t=1721041621\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018830/extras/3501515a1dbd7a6b9f1eaae96d88146c.webm?t=1721041621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018830/extras/3501515a1dbd7a6b9f1eaae96d88146c.mp4?t=1721041621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018830/extras/be44f96f4fa16c62f7a8d3cf3d49d481.avif?t=1721041621\" width=666 height=66 /></span><br><br><strong>Your goal is to find the key to the locked door to get out of the house. A crazy Kawaii girl will stop you from doing this. For a while, you can hide from her in a barn chest, under a bed or in a closet, but in general, if she notices you, you better run. </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018830/extras/62b7185ee28546368119d5634922a344.poster.avif?t=1721041621\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018830/extras/62b7185ee28546368119d5634922a344.webm?t=1721041621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018830/extras/62b7185ee28546368119d5634922a344.mp4?t=1721041621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></spa